msgid ""
"Add the following right under ``Clone.BULLET_DAMAGE = DAMAGE``: "
"``ammo_in_weapon -= 1``"
msgstr ""
"Ajoutez ce qui suit juste en dessous : ``Clone.BULLET_DAMAGE = DAMAGE`` : "
"``ammo_in_weapon -= 1``"

